<div class="help-content-wrap"><h3 id="stay-in-control-it-s-only-a-game">Stay in Control, It&#39;s Only a Game</h3>
<p>We believe that gaming should always be an enjoyable activity and our customers can have fun from betting. Please kindly remember these following tips, it may help you to keep in control and make sure gaming will not become a problem.</p>
<ol>
<li>Only place bets with amounts that you can afford to lose.</li>
<li>Gambling should be entertaining and not be seen as a way of making money.</li>
<li>Bet sensibly and never chase your losses.</li>
<li>Keep track of the time and amount you spend.</li>
<li>Balance gambling with other activities. Think about if you are still having fun from betting if gaming is your only entertainment.</li>
<li>Take regular breaks from gambling. You can use your self-exclusion option and our well-trained staff will call you to confirm your decision.</li>
<li>Don’t gamble when under the abnormal conditions such as alcohol or when you’re upset.</li>
</ol>
</div>